dc_title_s: Electric Power Substations: United States, Summer 2014
dc_description_s: This point shapefile provides the location, current and previous owners, maximum kilovolts of power, operational status, and other infomation for electric power substations in the United States. This layer is part of a collection of GIS data for renewable and electric energy in the U.S. This layer is from the 2014 Summer Quarter update (Update 1016).This layer can be used for locating electric power substations within the United States.
